<h3 style="color: #70AD47;">AssessmentImageBehavior <a href="components/AssessmentImageBehavior.php">components/AssessmentImageBehavior.php</a></h3>

<strong>Purpose:</strong> Evidence image management and validation

<strong>Constraints:</strong></ul><li>Maximum 5 images per assessment</li><li>Allowed formats: jpg, jpeg, png, gif, webp</li></ul></ul><li>Maximum size: 5MB per image</li><li>Storage: `/web/uploads/assessments/{assessment_id}/`</li></ul>

<strong>Key Methods:</strong>
```php
static::uploadImages(Assessment, UploadedFile[]) : array
static::getImages($assessmentId) : array
static::deleteImage($assessmentId, $filename) : bool
static::getUploadDir($assessmentId) : string
static::getUploadUrl($assessmentId) : string
```

<strong>File Naming:</strong> `image<em>{timestamp}</em>{randomInt}.{ext}`

<strong>Usage Example:</strong>
```php
$files = UploadedFile::getInstances($model, &#039;images&#039;);
$uploaded = AssessmentImageBehavior::uploadImages($assessment, $files);
```

