<strong>Purpose:</strong> Track assessment submission and validation workflow

<h4 style="color: #4F81BD;">Zone/School Assignment:</h4></ul><li>`m260402<em>114038</em>add<em>zone</em>school<em>to</em>users` - Adds `zone<em>id`, `school</em>id` columns to users</li></ul>

<strong>Purpose:</strong> Support zone/school-based access control

<h4 style="color: #4F81BD;">Examiner/Validator Assignment:</h4><ul><li>`m260403<em>110000</em>backfill<em>assessment</em>examiner<em>user</em>id` - Populates examiner relationship</li></ul></ul><li>`m260403<em>add</em>validated<em>by</em>to<em>assessment` - Adds `validated</em>by`, `validated_at` columns</li></ul>

